{"type": "article", "id": 57445, "title": "五芳斋重阳节广告很 80 年代，Burberry 开 24 小时限时精品店 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-10-18T05:24:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 64, "name": "广告"}, {"id": 189, "name": "Burberry"}, {"id": 330, "name": "可口可乐"}, {"id": 26515, "name": "五芳斋"}, {"id": 1319, "name": "苏铭天"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 103970, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 50, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181018130323HgDTX3unpJ6yPm2v.png", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/42055.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">张若昀、许晴代言羽西</a>，并在朋友圈投放了广告。</strong><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181018122706uKrOGt0csNgApXYf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.468750\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181018122750BFDEVCcIMvy0JqZm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.932000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>又是跨界</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.linkshop.com.cn/web/archives/2018/411643.shtml?sf=wd_search\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>可口可乐将为天猫双 11 推出定制专属生产线。</strong></a>定制礼盒限量 30000 瓶，于 10 月 20 号起登陆天猫旗舰店预售，消费者可以根据自己喜爱的口味进行定制。</p><p>此前可口可乐在天猫已经上线了 <a href=\"https://detail.tmall.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.1-b-s.w5001-16698235779.2.ec895b29Zn7YsI&amp;id=572832928473&amp;rn=113538323189fa3fd1be68964d8d8c07&amp;abbucket=3&amp;scene=taobao_shop\" rel=\"nofollow\">FIFA 定制瓶</a>服务。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181018123317s2Jf9UKcuEzWGoDg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.015152\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181018123320FmYfWrPoSG69qlc2.png\" data-ratio=\"0.954654\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><h3>值得一提的 Case</h3><p><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/zGIWc_FZTlsMRk9LRl6QWQ\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>10 月 17 日，Burberry 在小程序开启限时 24 小时精品店</strong></a>，发售一款 T 恤和卫衣。此后每个月的 17 日，Burberry 都会按照街头潮牌 Drop 的模式进行限量发售若干服装。这是新创意总监上任后的又一变化。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018101812392754jvBLtqTim2EJWc.gif\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"gif\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4296050015277566?\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>五芳斋重阳节 80 年代复古广告，画面、配音都很地道</strong></a>。目前官宣微博转发 2680 次，还有更多其他营销号的转发，总播放量超过 400 万，效果不错，代理公司是环时互动。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=j0749i1io91\"></iframe> </figure>  </div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181018125131tBYOuxTmPJHUEM8z.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.887676\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181018125758ZW9vXINCp475dsF1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.778261\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181018125835JOgVaBmo0E6k1CxA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.778261\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810181258358EfbI4POQcMkqiG2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.776812\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181018125835Mc9C8PKiufoGhX7I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.778261\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><b><a href=\"https://www.adweek.com/brand-marketing/can-a-hamburger-give-you-nightmares-burger-king-tested-its-horrifying-new-creation-to-find-out/\" rel=\"nofollow\">汉堡王在美国推出万圣节特制汉堡：梦魇王</a>。</b>据广告（胡扯）说吃了之后做噩梦的几率高了 3.5 倍。梦魇王将于 10 月 22 日至 10 月 25 日在汉堡王餐厅供应。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181018124559rlIehxp5qP1O4Ucy.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h6>其他，也挺重要</h6><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 19.0px; font: 13.0px 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 19.0px; font: 13.0px 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #000000; min-height: 15.0px} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"http://www.adquan.com/post-2-46186.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>阿里巴巴旗下广告营销平台“阿里妈妈”发布信息流营销产品</b></a>。阿里妈妈信息流营销主要是在用户的商品信息流中穿插商家推广的商品，其展现形式包括图文、视频、清单等淘系内的原生内容，展现位置包括手机淘宝首页、用户购物车下方、收藏夹、支付成功页、订单页、物流页等，覆盖用户购前、购中和购后的场景。</p><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"https://adage.com/article/agency-news/sorrell-s4-capital-a-coconut-snubbing-creativity/315303/\" rel=\"nofollow\">苏铭天又谈了谈新公司。</a></b>马丁爵士表示，S4 Capital 的重点是内容，第一方数据、数字媒体购买和规划。</p><p>“有创意记者，有创意数据分析师，有创意媒体人，有做创意数据的人，甚至有创意的金融人士，”他说。“我们所谈论的是最广泛意义上的创造力。” 他说，创造力并没有在 S4 Capital 中扮演重要角色，或者说像这样的公司是错误的。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.brandchannel.com/2018/10/17/harrys-flamingo-for-women/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>时髦的互联网剃须刀品牌 Harry's 推出女性除毛产品线&nbsp;Flamingo</b></a>，设计依然很漂亮。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181018125331FJVgMvTSIpXuZjWx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.949000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181018125331vtFL4QKMn5ShkfXY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.865000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">题图来自 五芳斋</p>"}